  • Classes in cps.mouradalpha.interfaces used by cps.mouradalpha.components 
    Class Description
    ManagementCI  
    ManagementImplementationI
    The interface ManagementImplementationI defines the methods for handling topics.
    MessageFilterI
    The interface MessageFilterI is a FunctionalInterface that can be implementing with a class or a lambda expression, it's used by a Consumer in order to filter messages published in a specific topic
    MessageI
    The interface MessageI represent the specification the message used in this project, it contains the methods for handling Message.
    NotificationCI
    The interface NotificationCI defines the methods that allows the brokers to notify each other when a change is happened.
    PublicationCI  
    PublicationImplementationI
    The interface PublicationImplementationI defines the methods that allows to a Publisher to publish messages for a specific topic.
    ReceptionCI  
    ReceptionImplementationI
    The interface ReceptionImplementationI defines the methods that allows to a Subscriber to get messages for the topics that he subscribed.
    SubscriptionImplementationI
    The interface SubscriptionImplementationI defines the methods that allows to a Subscriber to subscribe for a topic.
